results.name: Square array read by antidiagonals in which row n lists the parts of the infinite n-th zone of the shell model of partitions, in nonincreasing order.
comment: The n-th zone of the shell model of partitions is formed by the parts of the n-th row of triangle A210941 together with infinitely many parts of size 1.
link: Omar E. Pol, Illustration of the partitions and regions of n, for n = 1..12
results.author: _Omar E. Pol_, Apr 19 2012
